definition: to agree (to do sth)/should/ought to/must/(legal) shall
to answer/to respond/to comply with/to deal or cope with

sentences.english: Concreting technology for the box girders and construction method for the prestressing system are dealt with as well.
sentences.chinese: 并介绍了箱梁混凝土的浇注工艺及预应力施工的方法。

sentences.english: The prestress method should be developed in the study of the rotor dynamics problems.
sentences.chinese: 预应力法在转子动力学问题的研究中可进一步拓展。

sentences.english: Anchor rope distribution is the key point in prestressed floodgate room design.
sentences.chinese: 锚索布置是预应力闸室设计的关键所在。

sentences.english: Lin Hai bridge is a cable-stayed bridge with a single pylon and one cable plane.
sentences.chinese: 临海大桥是一座独塔单索面预应力混凝土抖拉桥。

sentences.english: Prestress concrete beam uses C50 concrete usually.
sentences.chinese: 预应力混凝土梁中通常采用C50混凝土。

sentences.english: This paper retrospects the history and present state of the prestressed concrete continuous box girder bridge.
sentences.chinese: 本文回顾了预应力混凝土连续梁桥的发展历史与现状。

sentences.english: In this paper, the technique and calculation of beams strengthened by prestressing method are studied.
sentences.chinese: 本文研究了用预应力法加固梁的工艺和计算。

sentences.english: Bow-style pre-stressed beam is a new type of pre-stressed steel structure.
sentences.chinese: 弓式张弦粱结构是一种新型的预应力钢结构体系。

sentences.english: Pre-stress must be inflicted during the cable net construction.
sentences.chinese: 索网在建设时必须施加预应力。

sentences.english: A great amount of post tensioned pre-stressing concrete single box beam for double track (as called the Box Beam hereinafter) has been used on the line.
sentences.chinese: 该线大量采用后张法预应力混凝土双线单箱简支箱梁。

sentences.english: The secondary moment of prestressed concrete frame is different from that of continuous beam.
sentences.chinese: 预应力框架次弯矩与连续梁相比有着自己的特点。

sentences.english: SRAP external prestressed reinforcement is a new bridge reinforcement technology.
sentences.chinese: SRAP体外预应力加固是一种新的桥梁加固技术。

sentences.english: A new layout of prestressed cables in concrete frame spandrel beams is present.
sentences.chinese: 提出一种混凝土框架边梁预应力筋的新束型。

sentences.english: Suitable calibrated dynamometers were used to control the pull in the prestressing cables.
sentences.chinese: 用合适的率定过的量测计控制预应力钢索的拉力。

sentences.english: The stressed-arch frame is a new type of prestressed steel structure system.
sentences.chinese: 张拉弦钢拱架结构是一种新型的预应力钢结构体系。

sentences.english: Excessive midspan lag is one of the main problems of large span prestressed concrete girder bridges.
sentences.chinese: 跨中下挠过大是大跨预应力混凝土梁桥的常见病害。

definition: to support/to bear the weight of (a building)
